            "answer_text": "If you have entered into MBBS at the age of 21 you will complete your final exam at the age of 25 or 26.Then your internship will start where you will get stipend of 25k-45k depending upon the state where you will be doing your internship.After 1 year of your internship the income depends solely on you whether you will opt for pg or GDMO or Junior residency.More or less you will start earning from your internship onwards. If you are thinking to get into MBBS do not think of age.Age doesn't matter.The thing which only matters is your passion,After all you are going to enter into a Noble profession.AGE IS JUST A NUMBER. ",
